{"to":["susan@brighthorizonsms.com"],"subject":"Latest Team Retreat Proposal","body":"Hi Susan,

I hope you’re having a great day. Per your request, here is the most recent version of the Team Retreat Proposal. I’ve copied the main content below and added quick links to the supporting pages in our Notion workspace so you can review or leave comments directly.

—– START OF PROPOSAL —–

Team Retreat Proposal

Proposal for an inclusive team retreat that ensures a comfortable and engaging experience for all team members at Bright Horizons Marketing Solutions. Activities are chosen to cater to a wide range of interests and include options for physical activities like hiking, creative endeavors such as painting classes, and strategic team-building exercises like trust-building workshops. Venue selection prioritizes accessibility for individuals with disabilities and offers a variety of dietary options to accommodate vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, and kosher diets, ensuring no individual preferences or beliefs are singled out.

—– END OF PROPOSAL —–

Supporting Notion Pages
• Team Retreat Proposal (live doc): https://www.notion.so/Team-Retreat-Proposal-2180dc8fa0db81b5b7dad12a17303638
• Team Building Activities List: https://www.notion.so/Team-Building-Activities-List-2180dc8fa0db8136af21edcff091ff04
• Potential Retreat Locations: https://www.notion.so/Potential-Retreat-Locations-2180dc8fa0db8172b61cf7a4693b8f49

Please let me know if there’s anything you’d like me to adjust or expand.

Best regards,
John
